name: arr-filter-function
description: Fast filter array to have only function values. But also allow you to give iterator function which will be called on each element of the array that is function - much like array.map functionallity. Useful when you want to filter, but also want to map in same time if needed.
author: Charlike Mike Reagent <@tunnckoCore> (http://www.tunnckocore.tk)
